== Amateka ==


=== Imyaka yo hambere hamwe namateka ===
Butera  <ref>http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/69290</ref> yavukiye mu [[Akarere ka Ruhango|Karere ka Ruhango]],  Akaba umwana w'ikinege wa Jean-Marie Vianney Butera na Marie Claire Uyambaje, bombi bakaba barapfuye. Nyina yahoze ari umuririmbyi wambere muri korari y'itorero ry'Abadiventisti b'umunsi wa Karindwi . Butera yize amashuri abanza ya ESCAF i Nyamirambo, APARUDE yisumbuye i Ruhango na APACE yisumbuye i [[Kigali]] Akaba yarize Ikorana Buhanga . Akaba Yari umwe muro korsri yo muri APACE .Mu mwaka wa 2012, yatangiye kwiga kaminuza muri Kigali Institute of Science and Technology . <ref name="bio">https://web.archive.org/web/20120110120556/http://tukabyine.com/index.php/articles/knowles-rwandas-true-music-diva</ref>

Muri 2019, nibwo yasozaga  MBA muri kaminuza ya gikirisitu ya Oklahoma . Akaba numubyeyi w'abakobwa babiri witwa Ora & Inzora Butera.

=== Umwuga wa muzika ===
Knowless yashyize ahagaragara alubumu ye ya mbere, ''Komeza'', mu Kuboza 2011.  Album ye ya kabiri, ''Uwo Ndiwe'', yasohotse muri Werurwe 2013. <ref name="salax2">http://focus.rw/wp/2013/04/action-packed-female-stars-take-over-rwanda/</ref> Knowless acungwa munsi ya label ya Kina Muzika. <ref name="chimp">http://chimpreports.com/index.php/entertainment/12109-riderman-wins-rwanda-talent-search.html</ref>

Yakinnye mu Rwanda no mu bihugu duturanye, harimo na Uganda,  kandi akorana n'abahanzi benshi, barimo Abanyarwanda Danny, Paccy, Ciney, Jay Polly, Kamichi na Urban Boyz, hamwe n'itsinda rya Vampos rya Uganda. Yise umuhanzi Cecile Kayirebwa w’umunyarwanda ukomoka mu Bubiligi n’umwanditsi w’indirimbo w’umunyamerika R&B, Brandy Norwood .  muri 2021 yasohoye alubumu nshya yitwa INZORA. <ref>https://www.ktpress.rw/2021/06/knowless-set-to-release-inzora-her-best-album-ever/</ref>

== Ibihembo ==
Knowless yatsindiye "Umuhanzi mushya mwiza" mumarushanwa ya Salax Awards 2010.  Muri Kanama 2013, yegukanye umwanya wa gatatu mu marushanwa ngarukamwaka ya Primus Guma Guma Super Star, abera kuri [[Stade Amahoro]] . <ref>http://chimpreports.com/index.php/entertainment/12109-riderman-wins-rwanda-talent-search.html</ref> Muri Werurwe 2013 yatsindiye igihembo cye cya kabiri cya Salax, kuri iyi nshuro mu cyiciro cy "Umuhanzi w’umugore mwiza". 

